## Purpose-
##       Describe subdirectory content.
##
## Last change date-
##       2020/01/19
##
## Implementation notes-
##       This subdirectory contains suggested content for your $HOME directory.
##       Put edited versions of these control files your $HOME directory.
##
## Usage notes-
##       .bash_history -> /etc/RO is used to disable bash history recording.
##       To create /etc/RO:
##           sudo touch /etc/RO
##           sudo chmod a=r /etc/RO
##
##       .bash_logout is not included. It is unchanged from whatever version
##       is provided by your distribution.
##
##       .gitconfig ** REQUIRES USER MODIFICATION **
